mai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587350/extras/2d5830a424ae92b9925b92ff53b28347.mp4?t=1661307645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chemistry knowledge is not necessary</h2><br>No knowledge of chemistry is required<br><br>Vick Scientist is assembled in a simple and intuitive way for you to learn while playing<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various types of atoms</h2><br>There are 5 different types of atoms that assemble different combinations of molecules<br><br>Throughout the game you will discover new molecules and learn how to assemble some that you already know<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587350/extras/274637a3080c45536889509f1600165c.avif?t=1661307645\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original soundtrack: soundtrack prepared exclusively<br></li><li>52 Levels assembled progressively, so you can learn while playing<br></li><li>Minimalist Design: No punctuation, no timer and no pressure. Enjoy the puzzles and solve in your time</li></ul>",
